sets.title: Alert
sets.group: The instrument has encountered a temporary condition that is preventing the unit from performing breath analysis. The alert will clear automatically.
sets.status: Liquid is detected in the breath sample system. This must dry before the instrument can perform another test.
sets.status decription: Liquid is detected in the breath sample system. This must dry before the instrument can perform another test.

sets.title: Analysis Disabled
sets.group: Breath testing is disabled for a reason other than a fault or alert.
sets.status: Breath testing is disabled because a temporary error condition was detected.
sets.status decription: Breath testing is disabled because a temporary error condition was detected.

sets.title: Analysis Disabled
sets.group: Breath testing is disabled for a reason other than a fault or alert.
sets.status: The instrument is not authorised to perform a test until a user code is entered, or an ID card is swiped, etc.
sets.status decription: The instrument is not authorised to perform a test until a user code is entered, or an ID card is swiped, etc.
